# This directory holds AI model weights.
#
# Contents (auto-downloaded on first startup):
#   best.pt        — YOLOv8s factory defect model (negi3961/factory-defect-guard)
#   best_v6_mc.pt  — MC Dropout variant (used in Sprint 4 for uncertainty estimation)
#
# The PredictionService will auto-download best.pt from HuggingFace Hub
# if it is not present. No manual download is needed.
#
# DO NOT commit .pt weight files to git.
# Add *.pt to .gitignore.
